      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for precise cam timing. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN variable M differential lock. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure internal longevity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry, offering exceptional feedback and mechanical grip. This is a mechanically sound driver's car with all major preventative maintenance addressed.",
